text: Nesse is a village in Dornum in Aurich, in Lower Saxony, Germany., United States National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency It is near the North Sea coast, about 2.5 km west of the village of Dornum, and 20 km north of the town of Aurich. ==Notes== Category:Towns and villages in East Frisia Category:Aurich (district)
title: Nesse, Dornum
